$interpreted: Pedestrian: Hey brat! Watch where you're going!
Clark: Rune! You're wound hasn't healed yet. Don't go running around~
Maria: R-R-R-R-Rune.
Clark: You're hurt worse than me. How are you moving so fast?
Clark: ...*sigh*...hmph! Sophie's not here so I've got to deal with all of this!
Maria: Detecting Clark is on the verge of collapse. Do n-n-n-n-n-n-not move.
Rune: I want to find...Sophie.
Clark: This guy, can he try just a bit to act like the injured? I can't even keep up.
Rune: I want to find...Sophie.
Clark: You don't know where she is. How are you going to find her?
Rune: I don't, so I must go.
Clark: Just can't get through to him...
Clark: In any case, come back with me first.
Rune: I want to find...Sophie.
Chief of Security: I've finally got you!
Chief of Security: If I bring you in, then I won't get my head handed to me!
Clark: Again? Spare me...
Maria: S-S-S-S-S-S-S-Spare me~~
Chief of Security: Even if you've got Feather Clan wings, there's no way you're escaping this time!
Rune: Purple...cloak...
Rune: Purple...not, enemies...?
???: I'm here to help, trust me!
Clark: Who with the what and the...*sigh*...what on earth is happening!?
Pedestrian: Fire!!!!! Everybody, run!!!
???: Follow me.
Chief of Security: They're getting away again!!!
Clark: ...*wince*...
Maria: C-C-C-C-C-Clark, are you okay-ay-ay-ay?
Clark: It's nothing. I just ran a little too fast. The wound on my stomach opened up again.
Rune: Clark, I am sorry...
Clark: Forget it. Just don't go running off again and we'll call it even.
Clark: ...And, even though I'm pretty sure asking is going to be an even bigger hassle...
Clark: May I ask who you are?
???: My name is Nikola. That you are all okay is marvelous.
Clark: "You all"...?
Nikola: I've been following you since the underground waterway.
Clark: Following!?
Rune: You..are an enemy!
Nikola: Please, wait. I have no ill intention. If I were your enemy, why would I have helped you escape?
Nikola: I am a subordinate of the High Priest Devious, but his experiments are simply too horrific. Someone must stop him!
Clark: ...So you came to us?
Clark: Perhaps you've come to the wrong place? As you can see, we're nothing but a pile of tattered rags.
Nikola: ——You're all that's left!!
Nikola: Have you seen General Lazer!? You're the only ones in the entire Desert Kingdom that dare to stand up to Devious!
Clark: ...I understand. Supposing that what you say is true, I'm afraid we'll still have to refuse, Mr. Nikola.
Nikola: Why!? Don't you want to stop Devious' wicked scheme?
Clark: Yes, we do. But desire and ability are two different things.
Clark: Besides the fact that you're highly suspicious, it's precisely due to the fact that we don't have the fighting power that we are where we are.
Nikola: I understand your concerns, but——
Clark: Sorry to interrupt, but our wounds have yet to heal. Let's wait until our comrades bring back reinforcements before getting back to you.
Nikola: ...Understood. Since this is the case, let's just act like I never said anything. I thought you wanted to save your companion, but I guess I was wrong.
Rune: Huh? Companion?
Nikola: As I understand it, the fellow named Sanchez is being held by Devious.
Rune: Sanchez! Is alive!?
Nikola: He is still alive, yes. But I can't assure you for how long...
Rune: I'll go with you!
Clark: Rune...ahhhh...!
Maria: C-C-Clark-k-k, be-be-be care-careful.
Clark: Rune, don't go! It's probably a trap! Did you forget about Sophie? What will she do if she comes back and sees that you're gone?
Rune: First, save Sanchez, then find Sophie.
Clark: Rune! You promised me you wouldn't go running around. Rune...!
Clark: Maria, help me up.
Maria: Must refuse. C-C-Clark-k-k is injured.
Clark: Please, Maria. Otherwise, I won't be able to explain this to Sophie.
Maria: Understood! Find Sophie~~~
Clark: No, not find Sophie. Find Rune!!
Maria: Heading out~~
